commit.message:
acinclude.m4 (GLIBCPP_ENABLE_PCH): Fix obvious error.


2003-07-01  Benjamin Kosnik  <bkoz@redhat.com>

	* acinclude.m4 (GLIBCPP_ENABLE_PCH): Fix obvious error.
	* aclocal.m4: Regenerated.

         AC_LANG_CPLUSPLUS

         AC_LANG_RESTORE
       ])
     fi
